msgstr "パケットの送信元/送信先ポートによる、許可/禁止"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><ul><li>
#: en/security/shb-firewalls.xml:72
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Allow or disallow packets based on protocol"
msgstr "パケットのプロトコルによる、許可/禁止"

#. type: Content of: <sections><section><body><ul><li>
#: en/security/shb-firewalls.xml:73
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Allow or disallow packets based on flags within a specific protocol"
